OL,3,CHow Natasha's Law could impact the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,FThe parents of a teenager who died
OL,7,Ffrom a severe food allergy are
OL,8,Fvisiting Jersey as part of their
OL,9,Fcampaign to introduce new legislation
OL,10,Fto the islands.
OL,12,FNadim and Tanya Ednan-Laperouse's
OL,13,Fdaughter Natasha died aged 15 after
OL,14,Fshe ate an improperly labelled
OL,15,Fbaguette in the UK which contained
OL,16,Fsesame.
