OL,3,CHow Natasha's Law could impact the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,FThe couple will speak at the Channel
OL,7,FIslands' first-ever Food Allergy
OL,8,FConference in Jersey on Monday 18
OL,9,FNovember about introducing Natasha's
OL,10,FLaw, which aims to strengthen food
OL,11,Flabelling.
OL,13,FNatasha's Law was implemented in the
OL,14,FUK in October 2021, requiring all food
OL,15,Fretailers to display full ingredient
OL,16,Fand allergen information on every food
OL,17,Fitem made on-site or pre-packed for
OL,18,Fdirect sale.
