OL,3,CHow Natasha's Law could impact the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,FThis includes sandwiches, cakes, and
OL,7,Fsalads, providing individuals with
OL,8,Ffood allergies with clear information
OL,9,Fabout what they are consuming.
OL,11,FNadim and Tanya founded The Natasha
OL,12,FAllergy Research Foundation in 2019
OL,13,Ffollowing Natasha's death and have
OL,14,Fannounced it will partner with The
OL,15,FJersey Food Allergy Group as part of
OL,16,Ftheir campaign.
