OL,3,CHow Natasha's Law could impact the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,FTanya and Nadim say: "For too long,
OL,7,Fpeople with food allergies in the
OL,8,FChannel Islands have failed to have
OL,9,Fthe protections afforded to their
OL,10,Fcounterparts just a few miles away in
OL,11,Fthe UK. This is unacceptable.
OL,13,F"Being such close neighbours, we
OL,14,Fbelieve legislation around food
OL,15,Flabelling should be in sync with the
OL,16,FUK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
