OL,3,CHow Natasha's Law could impact the
OL,4,CChannel Islands
OL,6,F"It would fall squarely onto the
OL,7,Fshoulders of someone who really did
OL,8,Fnot want to make a move in this area,
OL,9,Fit's just not right and so we are
OL,10,Fcalling on businesses and the
OL,11,Fgovernment to do the right thing."
OL,13,FThe Food Allergy Conference will host
OL,14,Fworld-leading medical professionals,
OL,15,Fcharitable organisations, industry
OL,16,Fexperts, food allergy advocates, and
OL,17,Fthose with lived experience.
OL,19,FIt will take place between 8:30am and
OL,20,F3pm at the St Helier Town Hall on
OL,21,FMonday 18 November.
